kompozer-*.ebuild file made by Dabrouch: http://www.gentoo.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?pid=4603#p4603
 * tested on x86 and amd64
 * to be put into the 'apps-editor' category of the ebuild tree
 * installs the appropriate language packs and dictionaries
 * does not add any entry to the desktop menu yet

See also: http://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=146761

